Download last version WordPress
Create a file on C:\xampp\htdocs\NAME-MAIN-FOLDER
Run Xampp
Create new DB
Import SQL 
Paste WordPress files com NAME-MAIN-FOLDER C:\xampp\htdocs
http://localhost/NAME-FILE-CREATE-IN-HTDOCS/wp-admin/setup-config.php 
Confirm that you don´t want to run an empty file, so the SQL that you want to access
When access, you have to choose a theme and that´s it!
